<topic id="author-finding-and-replacing-text">
  <title>Finding and Replacing Text</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Author Editor<indexterm>find/replace</indexterm></indexterm><indexterm>Find/Replace<indexterm>Author editor</indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>You can search for a specific word or string of characters using the following features:<ul>
        <li><xref href="find-replace-dialog.dita#find-replace-dialog"
            format="dita"><uicontrol>Find/Replace</uicontrol> dialog
          box</xref></li>
        <li product="author developer editor"><xref
            href="find-and-replace-text-in-files.dita#find-and-replace-text-in-files"
            format="dita"><uicontrol>Find/Replace in
              Files</uicontrol> dialog box</xref></li>
        <li><xref href="quick-find-toolbar.dita#quick-find-toolbar" format="dita"
              ><uicontrol>Quick Find</uicontrol> toolbar</xref></li>
        <li><xref href="find-all-elements-dialog.dita#find-all-elements-dialog"
            format="dita"><uicontrol>Find all Elements</uicontrol> dialog
            box</xref></li>
      </ul></p>
    <p>Complex search operations may take some time to complete. If a search operation takes more
      than 5 seconds, you are prompted to decide whether you want to continue the operation or stop
      it.</p>
  </body>
